560
00:28:50.996 --> 00:28:54.792
I got a gym membership
and a nutritionist. [chuckles]

561
00:28:55.626 --> 00:28:57.168
- What?
- No. it's...

562
00:28:57.169 --> 00:28:58.796
No. it's okay. You can say it.

563
00:29:00.339 --> 00:29:04.217
I guess I'm realizing
that you taking care of me

564
00:29:04.218 --> 00:29:06.679
probably got in the way
of you taking care of yourself.

565
00:29:08.305 --> 00:29:11.808
[chuckles] It's funny.
Bob says the same thing. [chuckles]

566
00:29:11.809 --> 00:29:14.102
- Bob from work?
- [both chuckle]

567
00:29:14.103 --> 00:29:16.938
You talking about me a lot
with your IRS colleagues? [chuckles]

568
00:29:16.939 --> 00:29:20.276
[chuckles] No. only the ones
who make me breakfast. [chuckles]

569
00:29:21.777 --> 00:29:23.737
Ah. Right.

570
00:29:24.780 --> 00:29:26.656
Can I. uh. can I see that?

571
00:29:26.657 --> 00:29:28.783
Oh. this is... [stutters] ...nothing.
I'm selling it.

572
00:29:28.784 --> 00:29:30.411
I-I know. I'm the one who's buying it.

573
00:29:31.579 --> 00:29:34.080
[chuckles] You listen
to <i>The Sicarius Files</i>?

574
00:29:34.081 --> 00:29:37.626
Just the last episode and you know.
I was impressed.

575
00:29:39.545 --> 00:29:42.422
And then I realized
that you met an actual serial killer

576
00:29:42.423 --> 00:29:44.507
and then I was kind of worried about you.

577
00:29:44.508 --> 00:29:48.179
So. I think I'm just trying
to make sure you're okay.

578
00:29:51.265 --> 00:29:52.599
Well. I don't know what to say.

579
00:29:52.600 --> 00:29:54.309
Say you'll give me a discount.

580
00:29:54.310 --> 00:29:56.352
Turns out my niece is a huge fan.

581
00:29:56.353 --> 00:29:59.398
so I'm trying to get
some... some cool auntie points.

582
00:30:00.024 --> 00:30:01.482
Come on.

583
00:30:01.483 --> 00:30:03.318
Look. Merino wool.

584
00:30:03.319 --> 00:30:05.279
Oh. thanks.

585
00:30:07.781 --> 00:30:08.991
Thank you.

586
00:30:10.117 --> 00:30:11.619
Wait. wait. wait. wait.

587
00:30:13.621 --> 00:30:18.541
Okay. so after the divorce.
you wanted nothing more to do with me.

588
00:30:18.542 --> 00:30:20.669
