591
00:30:27.843 --> 00:30:29.719
Who called you?

592
00:30:29.720 --> 00:30:32.056
I don't know. it was Lee something.

593
00:30:33.140 --> 00:30:35.684
- Lee Duval?
- Yeah. that's it. Do you know him?

594
00:30:36.769 --> 00:30:39.187
Yes. I do.

595
00:30:39.188 --> 00:30:41.482
Okay. Well. thanks.

596
00:30:43.067 --> 00:30:45.861
